com.digi.xbee.api.models

Enum XBeeProtocol

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<XBeeProtocol>
      • com.digi.xbee.api.models.XBeeProtocol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<XBeeProtocol>

    public enum XBeeProtocol
extends Enum<XBeeProtocol>
    Enumerates the available XBee protocols. The XBee protocol is determined by the combination of hardware and firmware of an XBee device.
